{"type":"message","id":"403a7280","parentId":"0dc1c0bf","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:05:11.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that the @ mention format is getting mangled. Let me check the feishu_send_group.mjs script to see how it handles the message content, and also look at how the subagent is constructing the command with escaped quotes.\n\nThe problem seems to be with how the at tag is being passed through the command line. The quotes inside the XML attribute are getting escaped or mangled when passed as a shell argument.\n\nLet me look at the script to understand the issue better.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，是引号转义的问题导致 `user_id=` 后面的引号没正确传进去。让我看看脚本怎么处理的。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_013owibMZg6wbxDbfdHQZ7ZC","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_group.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779156304182,"responseId":"chatcmpl-59d376df-f3af-456d-8183-e63385e2c48b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d06afd8","parentId":"403a7280","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:05:11.630Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013owibMZg6wbxDbfdHQZ7ZC","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 飞书群消息发送工具\n * 使用 OpenClaw 配置的 appId/appSecret 获取 tenant_access_token 后发送消息\n */\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVp…OGKv';\n\nasync function getTenantAccessToken() {\n  const res = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Get token failed: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  return data.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\n/**\n * 发送飞书群消息（富文本，支持 @ 提及）\n * @param {string} chatId - 群 chat_id，如 oc_xxx\n * @param {string} text - 消息文本（支持 <at user_id=\"xxx\">name</at> 格式）\n */\nexport async function sendGroupMessage(chatId, text) {\n  const token = await getTenantAccessToken();\n\n  const res = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=chat_id', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`,\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({\n      receive_id: chatId,\n      msg_type: 'text',\n      content: JSON.stringify({ text }),\n    }),\n  });\n\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Send message failed: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  return data.data?.message_id;\n}\n\n// 直接运行时的入口\nconst chatId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst text = process.argv[3] || '热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>';\n\nsendGroupMessage(chatId, text)\n  .then(msgId => {\n    console.log('发送成功！message_id:', msgId);\n  })\n  .catch(e => {\n    console.error('发送失败:', e.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  });\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779156311630}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a8cc0ac","parentId":"0d06afd8","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:05:23.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"脚本本身没问题，问题出在子 session 拼命令行时转义出错了。sub-agent 执行的命令是：\n\n```\nnode ... feishu_send_group.mjs oc_xxx \"热更已完成... <at user_id=\\\"ou_...\\\">...\"\n```\n\nPowerShell 里 `\\\"` 转义在双引号字符串内部并不可靠，导致引号丢失。\n\n**解决方案：** 让脚本自己构造消息，不通过命令行参数传 @ 文本，或者在脚本里加一个「发送热更通知」的专用命令。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_019T3uzoW6FbiGaMdS7B9yyK","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_group.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"// 直接运行时的入口\nconst chatId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst text = process.argv[3] || '热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>';\n\nsendGroupMessage(chatId, text)\n  .then(msgId => {\n    console.log('发送成功！message_id:', msgId);\n  })\n  .catch(e => {\n    console.error('发送失败:', e.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  });","newText":"// 预设消息模板（避免命令行引号转义问题）\nconst TEMPLATES = {\n  'hotupdate-ok': '热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>',\n  'hotupdate-fail': '❌ 热更流水线失败，请检查日志',\n};\n\n// 直接运行时的入口\nconst chatId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst rawText = process.argv[3] || 'hotupdate-ok';\n// 支持模板名或直接文本\nconst text = TEMPLATES[rawText] ?? rawText;\n\nsendGroupMessage(chatId, text)\n  .then(msgId => {\n    console.log('发送成功！message_id:', msgId);\n  })\n  .catch(e => {\n    console.error('发送失败:', e.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  });"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779156311631,"responseId":"chatcmpl-caa431b1-0ee3-4650-a35d-978dfb2dba86"}}
