{"type":"message","id":"b8075ecb","parentId":"1489f5b5","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:05:34.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在脚本支持模板名，子 session 只需传 `hotupdate-ok` 或 `hotupdate-fail`，不用在命令行里拼含引号的字符串：\n\n```\nnode scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok\n```\n\n同时更新一下 TOOLS.md 里子 session 的通知命令："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01YDzSjB6Z1Tj1wjXzxxcXRr","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**更新完成后:** 用 `node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs` 发群消息通知（不要用 sessions_send，那只能发私聊）。\n消息内容：`热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>`","newText":"**更新完成后:** 用 `node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs` 发群消息通知（不要用 sessions_send，那只能发私聊）。\n成功命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n失败命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-fail`\n⚠️ 不要在命令行里拼含引号的 @ 文本，改用模板名（hotupdate-ok / hotupdate-fail）避免转义问题"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779156323753,"responseId":"chatcmpl-70a70b15-3d01-4dd2-8b54-4477a3061cba"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba6fe01d","parentId":"b8075ecb","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:05:34.651Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01YDzSjB6Z1Tj1wjXzxxcXRr","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  73 \n  74 **反馈要求:** 每个步骤执行中状态变化都要通过飞书消息及时反馈，包括：开始执行、执行中（等待）、执行完成/失败。不要让主人干等。\n  75 \n  76 **更新完成后:** 用 `node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs` 发群消息通知（不要用 sessions_send，那只能发私聊）。\n- 77 消息内容：`热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>`\n+ 77 成功命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n+ 78 失败命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-fail`\n+ 79 ⚠️ 不要在命令行里拼含引号的 @ 文本，改用模板名（hotupdate-ok / hotupdate-fail）避免转义问题\n  78 \n  79 **实现方式:** 主 agent 只做快速操作（检查 + git pull），然后通过 sessions_spawn 创建 sub-agent 去跑 Unity 流水线。主 agent 立即释放，继续响应其他消息。sub-agent 在后台执行并监控日志，完成后自动汇报结果。\n  80 \n  81 **⚠️ 重要：sub-agent 必须通过 bat 文件执行，不要拼内联 PowerShell 命令！**\n     ...","firstChangedLine":77},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779156334651}}
