{"type":"message","id":"ea0b7e36","parentId":"c7879d7e","timestamp":"2026-05-19T03:09:05.812Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01FSHR23ru69rK6XAmZUmQJ3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.7 (eeef486) — I don't have opinions about tabs vs spaces. I have opinions about everything else.\n\nUsage: openclaw mcp serve [options]\n\nExpose OpenClaw channels over MCP stdio\n\nOptions:\n  --claude-channel-mode <mode>  Claude channel notification mode: auto, on, or\n                                off (default: \"auto\")\n  -h, --help                    Display help for command\n  --password ***         Gateway password (if required)\n  --password-file <path>        Read gateway password from file\n  --token ***               Gateway token (if required)\n  --token-file <path>           Read gateway token from file\n  --url <url>                   Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to\n                                gateway.remote.url when configured)\n  -v, --verbose                 Verbose logging to stderr (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1617,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.7 (eeef486) — I don't have opinions about tabs vs spaces. I have opinions about everything else.\n\nUsage: openclaw mcp serve [options]\n\nExpose OpenClaw channels over MCP stdio\n\nOptions:\n  --claude-channel-mode <mode>  Claude channel notification mode: auto, on, or\n                                off (default: \"auto\")\n  -h, --help                    Display help for command\n  --password <password>         Gateway password (if required)\n  --password-file <path>        Read gateway password from file\n  --token <token>               Gateway token (if required)\n  --token-file <path>           Read gateway token from file\n  --url <url>                   Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to\n                                gateway.remote.url when configured)\n  -v, --verbose                 Verbose logging to stderr (default: false)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779160145812}}
{"type":"message","id":"9155ca6b","parentId":"ea0b7e36","timestamp":"2026-05-19T03:09:14.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 自带 `mcp serve` 命令，可以通过 **stdio** 把自己暴露给 Cursor 作为 MCP Server！\n\n配置很简单，在 Cursor 的 MCP 设置里添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"command\": \"openclaw\",\n      \"args\": [\"mcp\", \"serve\"],\n      \"type\": \"stdio\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 打开 Cursor → `Ctrl+Shift+J`（Settings）→ 搜索 **MCP**\n2. 点 **Add new MCP server** 或直接编辑 `~/.cursor/mcp.json`\n3. 把上面的 JSON 加进去，保存\n\n配完之后 Cursor 的 Agent 就能直接调用我这边的飞书、文件、工具能力了。要我帮你写好配置文件直接放进去吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779160145813,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3afceaba-48cb-4fb1-a3e2-a5f2e35ac539"}}
