{"type":"message","id":"ffc36db8","parentId":"f718ba80","timestamp":"2026-05-19T03:19:17.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the TAPD keepalive system can save cookies for multiple accounts. Let me check the current keepalive script to understand how it works.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先看看现在的脚本结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_016yhfzexqg2ahEXzpgaxJq7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_keepalive.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779160753941,"responseId":"chatcmpl-298bf72c-fcb0-454a-91e0-a9f772fbbd07"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a84678a2","parentId":"ffc36db8","timestamp":"2026-05-19T03:19:18.012Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_016yhfzexqg2ahEXzpgaxJq7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// TAPD Keepalive Script\n// Loads cookies, hits the workspace dashboard to refresh server-side session,\n// then saves the new cookies back to tapd_cookies.json.\n// Run periodically (every 1-2 days) to keep login alive indefinitely.\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_storage.json');\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'tapd-keepalive-state.json');\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function () {}, csi: function () {}, app: {} };\n};\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: 'cookies_missing', at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  const oldCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(oldCookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n\n  try {\n    log('Visiting workspace dashboard...');\n    const resp = await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    const url = page.url();\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const status = resp?.status();\n    log(`HTTP ${status} | url=${url} | title=${title}`);\n\n    if (url.includes('login') || title.includes('登录') || title.includes('WAF')) {\n      log('❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login');\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Bonus: also poke story-list to make sure deep nav still works\n    await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/story/list', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    const newStorage = await ctx.storageState();\n\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    fs.writeFileSync(STORAGE_FILE, JSON.stringify(newStorage, null, 2));\n\n    // Find tapdsession expiry for state\n    const tapdsession = newCookies.find((c) => c.name === 'tapdsession');\n    const exp = tapdsession?.expires > 0\n      ? new Date(tapdsession.expires * 1000).toISOString()\n      : 'session';\n\n    log(`✅ Refreshed ${newCookies.length} cookies | tapdsession exp: ${exp}`);\n    writeState({\n      ok: true,\n      at: new Date().toISOString(),\n      cookieCount: newCookies.length,\n      tapdsessionExpires: exp,\n      title,\n    });\n\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(0);\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: e.message, at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779160758012}}
{"type":"message","id":"5770d557","parentId":"a84678a2","timestamp":"2026-05-19T03:19:26.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以支持，但目前脚本是硬编码单账号的。改造思路：\n\n**多账号方案：** 用账号名做文件名区分\n\n```\ntapd_cookies_叶枝君.json\ntapd_cookies_兵王.json\ntapd-keepalive-state_叶枝君.json\n...\n```\n\n脚本加一个 `--account` 参数，保活时遍历所有账号文件。\n\n---\n\n**问主人几个问题：**\n\n1. **哪些账号需要保活？** 就你自己，还是还有别的同事（兵王、小骑士等）？\n2. **其他账号的 cookie 怎么来？** 需要他们各自扫码登录一次，还是你统一管理？\n3. **提单时是用哪个账号提的？** 目前脚本保活的是你自己的账号，如果提单要用别人账号就要换。\n\n确认了再改，不想白写 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779160758013,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c18468b6-796e-4c20-bd82-0b2b684bbc21"}}
