{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\5723efa8-2be2-447f-942e-e6e2ab6826dd.jpg (image/jpeg) | C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\5723efa8-2be2-447f-942e-e6e2ab6826dd.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ff7d0049ca0b2142900fd69659\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-19 18:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b6ff7d0049ca0b2142900fd69659]\nYousan(叶枝君): ![image]\n搜索框不好用提个bug单给李胜飞\n搜索提个","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"f5307838","parentId":"5f610e7e","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:22:42.016Z"}
