{"type":"message","id":"fe7cd3da","parentId":"00502c77","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:37:08.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to use Playwright to open the DevOps pipeline page. Since it's an internal network page, I can try using Playwright locally to access it. Let me spin up a sub-agent for this since it'll take some time.\n\nActually, the user said \"打开一个playwright\" - they want me to open the page via Playwright and analyze the pipelines for the 1V1 module. Since this involves browser automation that will take time, I should spawn a sub-agent.\n\nLet me think about how to do this. I need to:\n1. Use Playwright to navigate to the DevOps page\n2. The page likely requires authentication (maybe SSO/cookie based)\n3. Look at the 1V1 related pipelines\n4. Report back the analysis\n\nSince the page is likely behind authentication, I may need to use headed mode or have the user log in. Let me create a sub-agent to handle this.\n\nActually, I should first check if Playwright is available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，开浏览器去看看 🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zXvbu7ORmPxjGQcz2Kz40661","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"const { chromium } = require('playwright'); console.log('playwright available');\" 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1346,"output":296,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34410,"cost":{"input":0.00018844,"output":0.00008288,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001188824}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779187024339,"responseId":"09fb28c9-401f-4869-bc98-1c9c48fe96df"}}
