{"type":"message","id":"a3e9861d","parentId":"b9b4aea3","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:37:15.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Playwright is available. Let me spawn a sub-agent to open the page with headed mode (the user needs to see/interact with the login). Actually, since it's a sub-agent in isolated mode, it won't have headed mode display. \n\nLet me think about this differently. The DevOps page is internal and likely requires SSO/cookie authentication. The user might already be logged in their browser. I could:\n\n1. Use headed mode (headless: false) - but the user is talking to me on Feishu, they can't see the headed browser\n2. Try to use existing cookies from their regular browser\n\nActually, looking at the URL (devops.devcloud.ztgame.com), this is ZTGame's DevOps platform. It might have a long-lived session. Let me try with headless first and see what happens. If it shows a login page, the user would need to log in.\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent to handle this task - it'll need to try accessing the page and report back. I'll set it to use headed mode since login might be needed.\n\nWait, but the sub-agent is running in the background. If it needs headed mode, the browser window will pop up on the user's machine. Let me try headless first and see what happens.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_L5GS0FDTZyc1sk441xW31747","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"devops-pipeline-analysis","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":300,"task":"使用 Playwright 打开并分析 DevOps 流水线页面。\n\n**URL：** https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 先用 `headless: true` 打开页面\n2. 如果跳转到登录页，则切换到 `headless: false`（headed 模式让用户手动登录）\n3. 登录成功后，寻找页面上与 **1V1** 相关的 pipeline（流水线）\n4. 分析内容：\n   - 有哪些 1V1 相关的流水线？\n   - 每条流水线最近一次执行状态（成功/失败/运行中）\n   - 构建配置摘要\n5. 如果遇到登录，等待用户登录后再继续\n\n**Playwright 脚本路径：** 直接在 exec 中写脚本\n\n**Cookie 信息：** 如果页面需要 SSO 登录，使用 headed 模式让用户手动操作。\n\n**输出格式：** 以 Markdown 列表汇报各流水线的状态和配置信息。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":9128,"output":586,"cacheRead":25216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34930,"cost":{"input":0.00127792,"output":0.00016408000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000706048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002148048}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779187028805,"responseId":"4bc29c30-bf13-4fe9-84f1-374638236868"}}
