{"type":"message","id":"25ea318a","parentId":"393d4719","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:44:02.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to further analyze the \"1v1-测试服\" pipeline in the DevOps system to understand how it works, so they can use it to update the QA server. This means I should use the saved cookies to explore the pipeline details - its configuration, triggers, build steps, parameters, etc.\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent with Playwright to explore the pipeline details.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，去探索一下 1v1-测试服流水线的详细配置 🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_aLDuqRSjFtGTcU8s466p0131","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"devops-pipeline-detail","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":300,"task":"使用 Playwright 分析 DevOps 平台中「1v1-测试服」流水线的详细配置。\n\n**URL：** https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines\n\n**已有 Cookie：** `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\devops_cookies.json`\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 用 headless: true 启动 Playwright，加载 devops_cookies.json 中的 cookies\n2. 访问 https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines\n3. 找到「1v1-测试服」流水线，点击进入详细页面\n4. 分析以下内容：\n   - **构建配置：** 构建步骤有哪些？每个步骤做什么？\n   - **触发方式：** 手动触发？自动触发（代码推送/定时）？\n   - **构建参数：** 需要哪些参数（如版本号、分支等）？\n   - **最近构建详情：** #1083 的详细构建日志摘要，看看每一步执行了什么命令\n   - **产物/输出：** 构建产出了什么？部署到哪里？\n   - **关联代码仓库：** 绑定的 Git 仓库和分支\n5. 保存页面截图以备参考\n\n**如果页面需要跳转到登录页：**\n- 先尝试用 cookies 登录\n- 如果 cookies 失效，用 headed: false 模式，通知用户手动登录\n\n**注意：** 详细分析所有能看到的配置信息，包括点击查看最近一次构建的详细步骤和日志。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3269,"output":534,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37595,"cost":{"input":0.00045766000000000003,"output":0.00014952000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000946176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001553356}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779187434990,"responseId":"43f99e08-9e80-4332-9a2a-fbe3182d9483"}}
