\\"DEVOPS_DONT_KILL_PROCESS_TREE\\\" \\\"true\\\"\\n# 这里通过 daemon.py 执行启动进程的脚本\\n# 如果直接执行会在流水线脚本执行完毕后退出\\ncd /data/${dest}\\npython stop.py server.json config.json\\nsleep 10\\npython run.py server.json config.json\\n```\\n- 先停止所有旧服务进程（`stop.py` 发 kill -15 信号）\\n- 等待 10 秒后用 `run.py` 启动所有服务\\n- 启动的微服务列表（#1083 日志）：\\n  - `statesvr` × 2（statesvr_1、statesvr_\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-proxy\",\n      \"model\": \"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"aborted\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779187727916,\n      \"responseId\": \"chatcmpl-d373417a-5c6a-4138-94bd-eaca340b3bf6\",\n      \"errorMessage\": \"Request was aborted\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"e96c5600\",\n        \"seq\": 28\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": true,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 53145\n}[... 34125 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["sessionKey","messages","truncated","droppedMessages","contentTruncated","contentRedacted","bytes"],"truncated":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779187756090}}
{"type":"message","id":"37e6115c","parentId":"0a7e7896","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:49:25.712Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sub-agent gathered extensive data. Let me compile all the information from its history into a comprehensive report for the user. The sub-agent has already collected data on:\n\n1. Pipeline basic info\n2. Variables\n3. Trigger settings\n4. All 3 steps: 打配置, build+替换, 重启服务\n5. Code source (GitLab)\n6. Each step's shell script configuration\n7. Build history\n\nLet me present this to the user in a clean format.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"信息量很大，我来整理汇报 🌸\n\n---\n\n## 「1v1-测试服」流水线完整分析\n\n### 📋 基本信息\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 描述 | 1v1测试服的维护 |\n| 最近构建 | #1083（19日18:10，敖亚军，2分钟✅）|\n| 总执行 | 1558次 |\n| 流水线ID | `p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a` |\n\n### 🎛️ 启动变量（启动新构建时需要填）\n\n| 变量名 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|-------|--------|------|\n| **`dest`** | `1v1_cehua2`（列表选择）| **目标目录** — 指定部署到哪个服务器目录 |\n| **`code_branch`** | `YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521` | 代码分支 |\n| **`battle_branch`** | 同上 | 战斗模块分支 |\n| **`config_branch`** | 同上 | 配置分支 |\n| **`manzo_branch`** | `main` | manzo 分支 |\n\n> 关键：`dest` 决定了部署到哪个服务器！目前常用的值比如 `1v1_cehua2`（策划测试服）、`1v1_qa`（QA测试服）\n\n### 🔧 构建步骤（Linux 机）\n\n**① 打配置**\n```bash\ncd /root/1v1/ && sh -x ./genConfig.sh ${config_branch} ${dest}\n```\n→ git pull 配置分支 → Luban 编译 Excel 配表 → 输出 `.bytes` 到目标目录\n\n**② build+替换**\n```bash\ncd /root/1v1/ && sh -x ./1v1.sh ${manzo_branch} ${code_branch} ${battle_branch} ${dest}\n```\n→ git pull 多个分支代码 → 编译 .NET 服务 → 复制 `.dll`/`.pdb` 到部署目录（涉及 roomsvr/Battle1V1/CardCommon 等）\n\n**③ 重启服务**\n```bash\ncd /data/${dest}\npython stop.py server.json config.json\nsleep 10\npython run.py server.json config.json\n```\n→ 停所有微服务 → 等10秒 → 启动微服务（statesvr/roomsvr/gatesvr/lobbysvr/proxysvr 等十几个）\n\n### 🔄 触发方式\n- ✅ **手动触发**（目前主要方式）\n- ❌ **远程触发**（已关闭但支持）\n- ❌ **定时触发**（无配置）\n- **代码源**：**GitLab**（但只读，无法在此修改）\n\n### 💡 如何用来更新 QA 服\n\n要更新 QA 服（而不是策划服），只需要在**启动新构建**时把 `dest` 改成 `1v1_qa` 即可：\n\n```\n启动变量：\n  dest = 1v1_qa               ← 关键！改成 QA 服目录\n  code_branch = YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521\n  battle_branch = YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521\n  config_branch = YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521\n  manzo_branch = main\n```\n\n要不要试试从这边直接发起一个构建？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":19782,"output":871,"cacheRead":37888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58541,"cost":{"input":0.0027694800000000004,"output":0.00024388000000000003,"cacheRead":0.001060864,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004074224}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779187756092,"responseId":"fd33d5c2-a135-4df8-a930-6f0377edbdad"}}
