{"type":"message","id":"2f1762cd","parentId":"4986a1d8","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:55:21.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to set up the DevOps cookie to be kept alive daily, similar to how we do it for TAPD. Let me:\n\n1. Create a keepalive script for the DevOps platform cookies\n2. Integrate it into the heartbeat system\n\nBut first let me wait for the sub-agent to finish the build trigger. Actually, the user sent this as a separate message while I was yielding. Let me handle both:\n\n1. First, I need to set up the DevOps cookie keepalive\n2. Then wait for the build trigger result\n\nLet me think about what's needed:\n\n1. Create a script like `scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs` that loads devops_cookies.json, visits the DevOps page, and saves refreshed cookies\n2. Add it to HEARTBEAT.md\n\nLet me do this now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，给 DevOps cookie 也加个保活 🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_fMF0osySHVb1OcnwQJo91983","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_keepalive.mjs","content":"// DevOps Cookie Keepalive Script\n// Loads cookies, visits the DevOps pipelines page to refresh server-side session,\n// then saves the new cookies back to devops_cookies.json.\n// Run periodically (every 1-2 days) to keep login alive.\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'devops_cookies.json');\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'devops-keepalive-state.json');\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: 'cookies_missing', at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  const oldCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    ignoreHTTPSErrors: true,\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(oldCookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n\n  try {\n    log('Visiting DevOps pipelines page...');\n    const resp = await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    const url = page.url();\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const status = resp?.status();\n    const bodyText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText.substring(0, 500));\n    log(`HTTP ${status} | url=${url} | title=${title}`);\n    log(`Body preview: ${bodyText.substring(0, 200)}`);\n\n    // Check if we got redirected to login\n    if (url.includes('login') || title.includes('登录') || title.includes('LOGIN') || bodyText.includes('登录')) {\n      log('❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login');\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Also visit the pipeline detail page to deepen the session\n    await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n\n    log(`✅ Refreshed ${newCookies.length} cookies`);\n    writeState({\n      ok: true,\n      at: new Date().toISOString(),\n      cookieCount: newCookies.length,\n      title,\n    });\n\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(0);\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: e.message, at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2013,"output":1287,"cacheRead":46592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49892,"cost":{"input":0.00028182,"output":0.00036036,"cacheRead":0.001304576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001946756}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779188112270,"responseId":"0f408a8b-029d-4b8b-986b-7252f5626896"}}
