{"type":"message","id":"e1288224","parentId":"8117319f","timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:55:26.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now let me update HEARTBEAT.md to include the DevOps keepalive check alongside the TAPD one.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cp2KXRLLZRzHEGuq8dCB3486","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## TAPD 登录保活（每天一次）\n\n每天检查一次 `memory/tapd-keepalive-state.json`：\n- 如果 `at` 字段距今 > 20 小时，跑 `node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`（在 workspace 目录下）\n- 跑完后看退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期，悄悄过（HEARTBEAT_OK）\n  - `1` → ❌ 登录已失效，**主动通知主人**需要重新扫码登录 TAPD\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件，下次再试\n\n保活原理：访问一次 workspace 主页，TAPD 会自动续 `tapdsession` 7 天。只要每周至少跑一次就能永久维持登录。","newText":"## 登录保活（每天一次）\n\n每天检查保活状态文件，如果距离上次执行 > 20 小时则自动执行。\n\n### TAPD 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新扫码登录 TAPD，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n\n### DevOps 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/devops-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新登录 DevOps，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/devops_cookies.json`\n\n**保活原理：** 访问一次页面，服务器端 session 会自动续期。"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":146,"output":607,"cacheRead":49792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50545,"cost":{"input":0.00002044,"output":0.00016996,"cacheRead":0.001394176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001584576}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779188121856,"responseId":"52c870fc-b27f-40c3-9bd6-7f20bcf75ab7"}}
