{"type":"message","id":"375ccc45","parentId":"63fff1db","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:01:47.918Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the SKILL.md for this skill.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_O92nJwQ6MwQLuTI9pREO5618","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\update-test-server\\SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: update-test-server\ndescription: Update the 1v1 test/QA server via DevOps CI/CD pipeline. Use when user says \"更新测试服\", \"更新qa服\", \"构建qa\", \"更新服务器\".\n---\n\n# 更新测试服服务器 (Update Test Server)\n\n通过 DevOps 流水线触发「1v1-测试服」构建，更新 QA/策划测试服。\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- **DevOps Cookie:** `workspace/devops_cookies.json`（需提前扫码登录保存）\n- **Playwright:** 已安装\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### 触发构建（默认 QA 服）\n\n```javascript\n// 参考脚本逻辑\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\n```\n\n### 操作步骤\n\n1. **读取 Cookie**：从 `workspace/devops_cookies.json` 加载\n2. **访问流水线**：`https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n3. **点击「启动新构建」**\n4. **设置目标参数**：\n   - `dest` = `1v1_qa`（QA 服）或 `1v1_cehua2`（策划测试服）\n   - `code_branch` / `battle_branch` / `config_branch` = 保持默认分支\n   - `manzo_branch` = 保持默认（main）\n5. **提交触发**并确认构建进入运行中状态\n6. **汇报结果**：返回构建编号和状态\n\n## Pipeline 详情\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 流水线名 | 1v1-测试服 |\n| 分组 | 1v1 |\n| Pipeline ID | `p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a` |\n| 描述 | 1v1测试服的维护 |\n| 当前版本 | 150+ |\n| 代码源 | GitLab（只读） |\n| 触发方式 | 手动触发 |\n\n### 构建步骤\n\n1. **打配置** — 拉配置分支 → Luban 编译 Excel 配表 → 输出到部署目录\n2. **build+替换** — 拉代码分支 → 编译 .NET 服务 → 复制 `.dll` 到部署目录\n3. **重启服务** — `stop.py` 停服务 → `run.py` 启动微服务\n\n### 启动变量\n\n| 变量名 | QA 服值 | 策划服值 | 说明 |\n|-------|---------|---------|------|\n| `dest` | `1v1_qa` | `1v1_cehua2` | **目标部署目录（关键参数）** |\n| `code_branch` | 默认分支 | 默认分支 | 代码分支 |\n| `battle_branch` | 默认分支 | 默认分支 | 战斗模块分支 |\n| `config_branch` | 默认分支 | 默认分支 | 配置分支 |\n| `manzo_branch` | `main` | `main` | manzo 分支 |\n\n## Cookie 保活\n\nDevOps cookie 会自动保活（每天一次），无需手动重新登录。\n\n## 通知\n\n构建完成后，通过飞书群消息通知相关同事。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 触发后构建大约需要 **2 分钟**完成\n- `dest` 参数决定部署到哪个服务器，默认为 QA 服（`1v1_qa`）\n- 如果 cookies 失效，需要带 `headless: false` 重新扫码登录\n- Pipeline 页面不支持修改配置（只读权限）\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":106,"output":894,"cacheRead":52736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53736,"cost":{"input":0.00001484,"output":0.00025032,"cacheRead":0.001476608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017417679999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779188497886,"responseId":"dae796bb-ee18-41e8-b79e-26e0e38bd08a"}}
