{"type":"message","id":"1c899d2e","parentId":"0130fb7a","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:11:04.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the edit failed error I got earlier when I tried to update TOOLS.md. Let me explain what happened.\n\nThe error was:\n\n```\nValidation failed for tool \"edit\":\n  - path: must have required properties path\n  - root: must not have additional properties\n  - edits.0.oldText: must have required properties oldText\n```\n\nThis happened because I included `\"oldText\"` at the wrong level - I put it outside the edits array instead of inside each edit object. Let me explain this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"就是之前改 TOOLS.md 时我写错了参数结构 😅\n\n**错误写法**（我犯的）：\n```json\n{\n  \"edits\": [...],\n  \"oldText\": \"xxx\",   // ← 放错位置了！\n  \"newText\": \"xxx\"    // ← 放错位置了！\n}\n```\n\n**正确写法**（`oldText`和`newText`要包在 `edits` 数组里）：\n```json\n{\n  \"path\": \"TOOLS.md\",\n  \"edits\": [{\n    \"oldText\": \"xxx\",\n    \"newText\": \"xxx\"\n  }]\n}\n```\n\n简单说就是我写太快漏了 `path`，又把 `oldText/newText` 放在了 `edits` 外面。后来重写一遍就好了，已经是正确的样子了～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":57723,"output":291,"cacheRead":1920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59934,"cost":{"input":0.00808122,"output":0.00008148,"cacheRead":0.00005376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00821646}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779189058238,"responseId":"1b1e8ea2-53d6-4ffe-ac39-c29a2ff08f5e"}}
