{"type":"message","id":"41facb2d","parentId":"e73a6421","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:15:20.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that the DevOps pipeline \"1v1-测试服\" is for updating the server-side (服务端), not the client. And after it succeeds, I should also notify the group chat to @兵王(周以天), similar to how the Unity hotupdate pipeline does it.\n\nWait, actually they said \"成功以后@通知叫你的人\" - I think they mean after the build succeeds, I should @notify the relevant people (兵王/周以天). Or could \"叫你的人\" mean \"call your people\" - maybe they want me to notify the dev group?\n\nActually re-reading: \"这个是更新服务端的，成功以后@通知叫你的人\" - \"this is for updating the server side, after success @notify your people\". Hmm, \"叫你的人\" - I think this might mean notify people in the dev group who would need to know. Or maybe it's a typo and they mean \"通知有关的人\" or \"通知群里的人\".\n\nLooking at the existing flow, when Unity hotupdate is done, I send a message to the CCG dev group. So for the DevOps pipeline (server-side update), they also want a notification in the group when it completes.\n\nThe build #1084 is currently running. I should check its status and then send a notification if it completed.\n\nLet me check the build status first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！这是更新服务端的，完成后在群里 @兵王 通知。让我看看 #1084 跑完没："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jx2cWCXtd9mmaFFVMM9v2529","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"check-build-status","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":120,"task":"使用 Playwright 检查 DevOps 构建 #1084 的状态。\n\n**已有 Cookie：** `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\devops_cookies.json`\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 加载 cookie，headless 访问 https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a?buildId=b-a872a3a41313452db446a47f694247f2\n2. 看最新的构建历史，找 #1084 的状态\n3. 汇报：#1084 是否已完成？成功还是失败？\n\n如果 cookie 失效，用 headless: false 让主人重新登录。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"de