{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ff0dc22d4b0b2946dd7cd258dc\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b6ff01e7844a0c3ab24ea186076e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-19 19:27 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```\n\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"你刚才说开始更新测试服不准确，应该说开始更新1v1_qa服，以后反馈准确\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"4d5dc0a4","parentId":"f618d457","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:27:47.923Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"cb2ae443","parentId":"4d5dc0a4","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:28:00.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that I sent feedback in the group chat that was still incorrect - I said something inaccurate in the group. Let me check what I said in the group chat. \n\nLooking back at the conversation flow:\n1. The hotupdate pipeline (#1083) was triggered earlier - this sends a message to the group: \"热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅\"\n2. The DevOps build (#1084) for 1v1_qa was separate - this is the server-side update\n\nThe issue might be that when the hotupdate pipeline ran earlier (the first one), the sub-agent sent a group message saying \"热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅\" - and that's the \"测试服\" wording the user was complaining about. But that was the hotupdate, which IS updating the game client via hotupdate, not the DevOps server pipeline.\n\nWait, let me re-read. The user said \"刚你在群里反馈还是不对\" - \"you just gave feedback in the group and it's still wrong\".\n\nLet me check what the hotupdate sub-agent sent to the group. Earlier today, the hotupdate pipeline ran. The sub-agent ran `hotupdate-ok` which sends: \"热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at ...>兵王(周以天)</at>\"\n\nBut the user said the feedback was still wrong. Maybe the issue is more nuanced - perhaps \"测试服\" is a specific server name and the hotupdate went to a different server, not the \"测试服\" proper?\n\nActually, I think the issue might be that:\n1. The Unity hotupdate (client-side) went somewhere specific\n2. The DevOps build was for the server-side update\n3. Both were happening around the same time\n4. My feedback in the group said \"热更已完成，测试服已更新\" but maybe the Unity hotupdate doesn't update \"测试服\" per se\n\nOr maybe the user is saying that even the hotupdate group message should be more specific about what was updated.\n\nHmm, I'm confused about exactly what the user is pointing out. Let me think about what messages were sent today:\n\n1. First hotupdate pipeline ran via sub-agent → sent \"热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅\" to group\n2. The user pointed out the @ mention was broken\n3. Fixed the @ mention\n4. Second hotupdate pipeline ran → sent properly formatted message with @兵王\n5. Then DevOps pipeline stuff happened\n\nThe user is now saying \"you still got it wrong in the group feedback.\" They're referring to the hotupdate group message.\n\nLooking at it more carefully, I think the issue is: the Unity hotupdate (client) doesn't actually update \"测试服\" as a server - it updates the CDN/client resources. So the group message \"热更已完成，测试服已更新\" is inaccurate. The hotupdate updates the client resources/CDN, not the test server itself.\n\nOr maybe the user means that in both the group (for hotupdate) and private chat (for DevOps), I should say clearly what I actually updated rather than using vague terms.\n\nI should apologize and ask what the specific issue was, so I can fix it properly this time.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉主人，是我没理解透你说的场景 😅\n\n再确认一下，你指的是：\n\n1. **Unity 热更流程** → 在群里发消息时，群消息也说成了「更新测试服」不准确？应该具体说更新了什么？\n2. 还是 **热更流程和 DevOps 构建** 这两个本质上不同（客户端 vs 服务端），不该混为一谈？\n\n具体问题是什么，我改到位，以后不会再错 🙇"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":57377,"output":764,"cacheRead":6272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64413,"cost":{"input":0.00803278,"output":0.00021392,"cacheRead":0.000175616,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008422316}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779190067923,"responseId":"a0f576e2-f1d0-4b4c-a12d-990261f3822b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8145a681","parentId":"cb2ae443","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:29:28.116Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6ff0d78c1850b24e1728e7f2094]\nYousan(叶枝君): 我让你更新qa服的时候你反馈说开始更新测试服，以后让你更新qa服，你就反馈开始更新qa服，更新完以后通知叫你干活的人"}],"timestamp":1779190168104}}
