hotupdate pipeline ran. The sub-agent ran `hotupdate-ok` which sends: \\\"热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at ...>兵王(周以天)</at>\\\"\\n\\nBut the user said the feedback was still wrong. Maybe the issue is more nuanced - perhaps \\\"测试服\\\" is a specific server name and the hotupdate went to a different server, not the \\\"测试服\\\" proper?\\n\\nActually, I think the issue might be that:\\n1. The Unity hotupdate (client-side) went somewhere specific\\n2. The DevOps build was for the server-side update\\n3. Both were happening around the same time\\n4. My feedback in the group said \\\"热更已完成，测试服已更新\\\" but maybe the Unity hotupdate doesn't update \\\"测试服\\\" per se\\n\\nOr maybe the user is saying that even the hotupdate group message should be more specific about what was updated.\\n\\nHmm, I'm confused about exactly what the user is pointing out. Let me think about what messages were sent today:\\n\\n1. First hotupdate pipeline ran via sub-agent → sent \\\"热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅\\\" to group\\n2. The user pointed out the @ mention was broken\\n3. Fixed the @ mention\\n4. Second hotupdate pipeline ran → sent properly formatted message with @兵王\\n5. Then DevOps pipeline stuff happened\\n\\nThe user is now saying \\\"you still got it wrong in the group feedback.\\\" They're referring to the hotupdate group message.\\n\\nLooking at it more carefully, I think the issue is: the Unity hotupdate (client) doesn't actually update \\\"测试服\\\" as a server - it updates the CDN/client resources. So the group message \\\"热更已完成，测试服已更新\\\" is inaccurate. The hotupdate updates the client resources/CDN, not the test server itself.\\n\\nOr maybe the user means that in both the group (for hotupdate) and private chat (for DevOps), I should say clearly what I actually updated rather than using vague terms.\\n\\nI should apologize and ask what the specific issue was, so I can fix it properly this time.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"抱歉主人，是我没理解透你说的场景 😅\\n\\n再确认一下，你指的是：\\n\\n1. **Unity 热更流程** → 在群里发消息时，群消息也说成了「更新测试服」不准确？应该具体说更新了什么？\\n2. 还是 **热更流程和 DevOps 构建** 这两个本质上不同（客户端 vs 服务端），不该混为一谈？\\n\\n具体问题是什么，我改到位，以后不会再错 🙇\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779190067923,\n      \"responseId\": \"a0f576e2-f1d0-4b4c-a12d-990261f3822b\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"cb2ae443\",\n        \"seq\": 201\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Yousan(叶枝君): 我让你更新qa服的时候你反馈说开始更新测试服，以后让你更新qa服，你就反馈开始更新qa服，更新完以后通知叫你干活的人\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1779190168104,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8145a681\",\n        \"seq\": 202\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\not a text message), the content might be in the form of structured JSON that OpenClaw processes. Let me check if there are any inbound media files or cached data.\\n\\nActually, I think the user might be talking about the `edit` tool error - I need to be more careful with the `path` parameter. And for the card template, since I can't see it, I should ask again or look for it differently.\\n\\nWait, let me re-read the flow:\\n1. User sent an interactive card message (from Feishu)\\n2. I replied saying I can't see the card\\n3. User replied \\\"又edit failed了，解决一下，更新技能和记忆\\\"\\n\\nSo the user is:\\n- Saying I made another \\\"edit failed\\\" mistake (referring to my earlier missing `path` bug)\\n- Wants me to fix it and update skill and memory\\n\\nBut the card template question is still unresolved. Let me address both:\\n1. For the edit failed - I need to be more careful with the `path` parameter\\n2. For the card template - I still can't see the card content\\n\\nActually, I think the user might be saying that the interactive card content IS the new notification template, and I should figure out how to use it. But without seeing the card content, I need to explain the situation.\\n\\nLet me look at the feishu_send_group.mjs to see if it supports card messages (msg_type: interactive) vs just text.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"主人，那个交互卡片我这边确实看不到内容 😅 飞书的消息卡片里是什么内容？是飞书的消息卡片 JSON 格式吗？\\n\\n不过我先同步问个关键问题：\\n\\n1. **卡片内容是什么？** — 比如标题、正文、颜色（绿色成功/红色失败）、@人这些\\n2. 你是想让我用卡片消息（`msg_type: interactive`）代替现在的纯文本消息来发群通知？\\n\\n如果能直接把卡片的 JSON 贴过来，我就能加到脚本里当模板用了～\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779190237696,\n      \"responseId\": \"2224746a-c41c-41c0-8c61-9d17a7129fb2\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"999b3979\",\n        \"seq\": 217\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Yousan(叶枝君): 就是你19:16分发给我的那个\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1779190429448,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"7b685686\",\n        \"seq\": 218\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user is referring to a message card they sent at 19:16. Let me check the chat history to find that card. I need to look at the recent messages from this session to find the card at 19:16.\\n\\nLooking back through the conversation, I need to find the message from 19:16. Let me check the session history.\\n\\nActually, looking at the conversation, I see the user sent a message at around 19:16 which was about \\\"这个作为通知模版\\\" replying to \\\"[Interactive Card]\\\". But I couldn't see the card content.\\n\\nWait - the user said \\\"就是