{"type":"message","id":"149caed0","parentId":"216e76b8","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:34:16.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the interactive card was sent by someone (maybe by the Feishu system or someone else) to the user at 19:16. It's in their direct chat with me (Feishu direct message). Let me check the direct chat, not the group chat.\n\nActually, looking at the message flow again. The user said \"就是你19:16分发给我的那个\". \"分发\" means \"distributed/sent to me\". So at 19:16, something was sent to the user in their direct chat (the Feishu robot chat with me). The message_id is `om_x100b6ff02707f0a0c2151ff6a40655c` (from the reply context).\n\nLet me try to fetch that specific message by its ID from the direct chat.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lzD9j4bGBtLTYRszOuuE1997","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// Fetch a specific Feishu message by ID to get the interactive card content\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVpthJUXVGYqT8eTVMc8t7DffxM1Z';\n\nasync function main() {\n  const tokenRes = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const tokenData = await tokenRes.json();\n  if (tokenData.code !== 0) { console.error('Token failed:', tokenData); return; }\n  const token = tokenData.tenant_access_token;\n  console.log('Token OK');\n\n  // Get message by ID\n  const msgId = 'om_x100b6ff02707f0a0c2151ff6a40655c';\n  const res = await fetch(\n    `https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages/${msgId}`,\n    { headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}` } }\n  );\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\n\nmain().catch(console.error);\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\fetch_