{"type":"message","id":"d063d2a4","parentId":"49b11712","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:34:39.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the interactive card message. The content is:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"title\": null,\n  \"elements\": [\n    [\n      {\n        \"tag\": \"img\",\n        \"image_key\": \"img_v3_02ad_e19fca1f-912a-450e-95de-3c229091b53g\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"tag\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"tag\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"\"\n      }\n    ]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThis card was sent by the app itself (cli_a9458ff380b99ccb) in chat `oc_3510070766baf929648c8ae79c6cfb15` at timestamp 1779189404999 (which is ~19:16 Beijing time).\n\nThe card contains:\n- An image with key `img_v3_02ad_e19fca1f-912a-450e-95de-3c229091b53g`\n- A text saying \"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\"\n- An empty text\n\nHmm, this looks like the card sent by the Unity hotupdate pipeline to the dev group chat. But it says \"请升级至最新版本客户端\" which means \"please upgrade to the latest client version to view content\". This is an auto-generated card by the Feishu bot, not a custom card.\n\nWait, actually this card was sent by the app bot (cli_a9458ff380b99ccb) to chat `oc_3510070766baf929648c8ae79c6cfb15`. This is a different chat from the dev group (oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77). So this is a private chat or another group.\n\nBut actually, `oc_3510070766baf929648c8ae79c6cfb15` - let me check. And the content says \"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\" - this is Feishu's standard message saying the client needs to be upgraded to view the content. So the actual card content is being filtered by Feishu because the user's client is not up to date, or the image_key is invalid/expired.\n\nWait, actually that doesn't make sense because the user received it and then replied to it saying \"这个作为通知模版\". So the user could see the card content on their end.\n\nThe card structure is simple:\n```json\n{\n  \"config\": {...},\n  \"elements\": [\n    [{\n      \"tag\": \"img\",\n      \"image_key\": \"img_v3_02ad_e19fca1f-912a-450e-95de-3c229091b53g\"\n    }, {\n      \"tag\": \"text\",\n      \"text\": \"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\"\n    }, {\n      \"tag\": \"text\",\n      \"text\": \"\"\n    }]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThe card the user sees on their phone might look different (with actual content because they have the latest client). The image_key might contain a screenshot or an actual card design.\n\nSince I can't see the actual visual card, I should describe what I found and ask the user to describe what the card looks like on their end, so I can recreate it as a notification template.\n\nActually, let me think about this more practically. The user wants to use an interactive card as the notification template instead of plain text. The Feishu interactive card format supports rich content. Since I couldn't see the actual card content (Feishu shows \"upgrade client\" placeholder), I need the user to describe it.\n\nLet me ask the user specifically what the card looks like - what text, colors, buttons it has.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了那张卡片！不过飞书 API 返回的内容显示的是「请升级至最新版本客户端」（可能是你的飞书版本比较新，卡片里有某些旧客户端不支持的格式）。\n\n卡片是发在群 `oc_3510070766baf929648c8ae79c6cfb15` 的，结构是一个图片 + 一段文字。\n\n**主人帮我描述一下那张卡片长什么样？** 比如：\n- ⬜ 是什么颜色的（绿色成功/红色失败）？\n- 📝 写了什么文字？\n- 🖼️ 图片是什么样的？\n- 有没有按钮？\n\n这样我就能把卡片 JSON 模板加到脚本里了～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":354,"output":955,"cacheRead":78720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80029,"cost":{"input":0.000049560000000000007,"output":0.0002674,"cacheRead":0.00220416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00252112}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779190467885,"responseId":"400a1508-c3e6-49af-8c9a-86ba0c1ed22c"}}
