{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ff0b3a9e080c44037892445dee\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-19 19:56 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"15bc2a45","parentId":"b54e765f","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:56:10.899Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"f5b52870","parentId":"15bc2a45","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:56:22.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the interactive card was sent directly to me (the bot) by them in our direct chat, not in a group. So the card was sent in the direct Feishu chat between Yousan and the bot.\n\nLet me look at the conversation more carefully. The message_id of the card is `om_x100b6ff02707f0a0c2151ff6a40655c`. The chat_id is `oc_3510070766baf929648c8ae79c6cfb15`.\n\nBut wait, looking at the conversation context, the user's messages that I've been receiving all have chat_type: \"direct\". So when the user says \"你单独发我的\" they mean the card was sent in our direct chat.\n\nActually, I think the issue is that the card message was sent BY the bot TO the user, not by the user. Looking at the sender info from the API response:\n```json\n\"sender\": {\n  \"id\": \"cli_a9458ff380b99ccb\",\n  \"id_type\": \"app_id\",\n  \"sender_type\": \"app\",\n  \"tenant_key\": \"2c5386f2a48e975d\"\n}\n```\n\nThe sender is the bot app itself (`cli_a9458ff380b99ccb`). So this card was sent BY the bot TO the user in chat `oc_3510070766baf929648c8ae79c6cfb15`. This chat might be the direct chat between the user and the bot.\n\nBut the content shows \"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\" which means the Feishu API is returning placeholder text instead of the actual card content, probably because the card contains some newer format elements.\n\nLet me think about what card could have been sent. The bot might have sent some kind of notification card with the hotupdate result.\n\nActually wait - I think I understand now. When the hotupdate pipeline ran, the sub-agent sent a message to the dev group using the `feishu_send_group.mjs` script. The script sends `msg_type: 'text'` messages. But maybe there was another card sent by the app through some other mechanism.\n\nOr maybe the user is referring to something completely different - the \"Interactive Card\" could be something the user sent to me in our direct chat that I processed but couldn't see the content of.\n\nActually, looking at the message flow more carefully:\n\n1. Earlier in the conversation, the user replied to \"[Interactive Card]\" saying \"这个作为通知模版\"\n2. The message_id of the card is `om_x100b6ff02707f0a0c2151ff6a40655c`\n3. The API shows the msg_type is \"interactive\" and the content is \"请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容\"\n4. The sender is the app itself (cli_a9458ff380b99ccb)\n\nSo the card was sent by the app/bot to the user, probably in their direct chat. The card content was something the user saw on their end, but when fetched via API, it shows the placeholder text because the actual card content might use newer Feishu card features.\n\nSince I can't get the actual card content from the API, and the user says \"你单独发我的\" (you sent it to me separately), I need to ask the user to describe what the card looks like so I can recreate it.\n\nBut actually - I wonder if the card was sent by the `feishu_send_group.mjs` script. Let me check - when I modified the script earlier, I added support for template names. But the card itself - could it have been sent by a different mechanism?\n\nActually, I think the simplest approach is to just ask the user what the card looks like so I can build the template. The API can't return the actual card JSON content.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，是机器人发给你的。但飞书 API 返回的卡片内容被截成了「请升级至最新版本客户端，以查看内容」的占位符，我拿不到完整的卡片 JSON 😅\n\n**最简单的方式：** 主人给我描述一下那张卡片长什么样？\n\n比如：\n```\n标题：[热更完成] / [构建成功] / ❌\n内容部位：写的是什么文字？\n颜色：绿色成功 / 红色失败？\n按钮：有没有？\n```\n\n或者如果你愿意，直接把卡片截图发我，我照着做一个卡片的 JSON 模板也行～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":10477,"output":935,"cacheRead":65792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77204,"cost":{"input":0.00146678,"output":0.0002618,"cacheRead":0.001842176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003570756}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779191770899,"respo