{"type":"message","id":"22d78931","parentId":"09c4bf7c","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:58:20.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to update the QA server. According to the rules we established:\n- Say \"更新qa服\" → feedback \"开始更新qa服\"\n- After completion → notify the person who asked (主人)\n\nLet me follow the process:\n1. Check if the DevOps pipeline cookies work\n2. Spawn a sub-agent to trigger the pipeline with dest=1v1_qa\n3. Notify the user when done","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，开始更新qa服 🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_c6L9tib4I5NQ3S1IqoN83571","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"trigger-qa-build","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":300,"task":"使用 Playwright 触发 DevOps 流水线「1v1-测试服」的构建，更新 QA 服。\n\n**目标：** 触发构建，设置 dest=1v1_qa，直接执行。\n\n**已有 Cookie：** `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\devops_cookies.json`\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 用 Playwright headless: true，加载 devops_cookies.json\n2. 访问 https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a\n3. 点击「启动新构建」按钮\n4. 把 dest 改为 1v1_qa，其他变量保持默认\n5. 点击提交/确定，直接触发构建\n6. 确认构建已进入运行中状态，获取构建编号\n7. 汇报：构建编号，是否已启动\n\n**如果 cookie 失效：** 切换 headless: false 让主人手动扫码登录后再继续。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":10509,"output":425,"cacheRead":65920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76854,"cost":{"input":0.00147126,"output":0.000119,"cacheRead":0.00184576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034360199999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779191894914,"responseId":"238d8c4b-f929-4984-a4ac-14c070d933de"}}
