{"type":"message","id":"60b50bae","parentId":"8d292a14","timestamp":"2026-05-19T11:59:23.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that when I refer to the pipeline, I should use the full server name from the DevOps pipeline. The pipeline name is \"1v1-测试服\" (not just \"测试服\" or \"qa服\"). So when I say \"开始更新qa服\", I should actually say something like \"开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服\" or similar. \n\nWait, let me re-read: \"以后回复的时候把流水线中的服务器名字说完整\" - \"In future replies, say the complete server name from the pipeline.\"\n\nThe DevOps pipeline is called \"1v1-测试服\" but the dest parameter determines which server gets updated. The actual servers are `1v1_qa` (QA服) or `1v1_cehua2` (策划服).\n\nI think the user wants me to include the full pipeline name when I reply. So instead of just \"开始更新qa服\", I should say something that includes \"1v1-测试服\" since that's the actual pipeline name.\n\nBut actually we also discussed earlier that:\n- 说「更新qa服」→ 反馈「开始更新qa服」\n- 说「更新测试服」→ 反馈「开始更新测试服」\n\nSo which is it? I think the user is clarifying - when mentioning the pipeline/server name, use the full name from DevOps, which is \"1v1-测试服\". But the dest target is different.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The user says \"把流水线中的服务器名字说完整\" - \"say the complete server name from the pipeline.\" The pipeline's server name is \"1v1-测试服\" (that's the pipeline group/folder name). So maybe:\n\nWhen they say \"更新qa服\", I should reply \"开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服\" or just \"开始更新qa服\" is fine but when mentioning the pipeline I should call it \"1v1-测试服\" not just \"测试服\".\n\nActually, I think the simplest interpretation is:\n- Don't say \"更新测试服\" when you mean the 1v1 pipeline\n- Say \"更新1v1-测试服\" for the full pipeline name\n- Combined with dest target: \"更新1v1-测试服流水线(qa服)\"\n\nLet me think about what concrete examples would look like:\n\nBefore (wrong):\n- \"开始更新测试服\"\n- \"开始更新qa服\"\n\nAfter (correct):\n- \"开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服\"\n- \"正在更新1v1-测试服(qa)\"\n\nHmm, or maybe the user just wants consistency - the pipeline is called \"1v1-测试服\", so I should say \"1v1-测试服\" not just \"测试服\". Like:\n\n\"开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标1v1_qa\"\n\nThat makes sense. The \"测试服\" name is ambiguous - there are many test servers. But the pipeline is specifically \"1v1-测试服\", so that's the exact name I should use.\n\nLet me update the relevant files and remember this rule going forward.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，流水线的全称是 **「1v1-测试服」**，不能说成简化的「测试服」。以后反馈时会说完整：\n\n- ✅ 「开始更新 **1v1-测试服** 流水线，目标 `1v1_qa`」\n- ✅ 「**1v1-测试服** 构建完成」"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_YdGGNtFDoTPKakeWSL1V7867","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**反馈规范:** 请求说什么服就反馈什么服。说「更新qa服」就反馈「开始更新qa服」，不要改说法。完成后通知指派人。","newText":"**反馈规范:** 请求说什么服就反馈什么服，不要改说法。完成后通知指派人。\n- 流水线全称是 **1v1-测试服**，反馈时必须说完整\n- 如「更新qa服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服」\n- 如「更新1v1_test服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标1v1_test服」"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1189,"output":967,"cacheRead":76032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78188,"cost":{"input":0.00016646,"output":0.00027076000000000004,"cacheRead":0.002128896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002566116}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779191952583,"responseId":"e620e03f-22fc-43a8-a904-94f251687d27"}}
