{"type":"message","id":"7cbfb3e7","parentId":"04ed17d9","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:00:41.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the user wants:\n- Don't say \"开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服\"\n- Just say directly: \"开始更新qa服\"\n\nSo the rule is simpler than I made it:\n- 请求说什么服 → 直接反馈什么服\n- \"更新qa服\" → \"开始更新qa服\"\n- \"更新测试服\" → \"开始更新测试服\" (different pipeline - Unity hotupdate)\n\nAnd the earlier point about \"说完整\" was just about not saying \"测试服\" when they said \"qa服\". So the original rule was correct all along - just mirror what they say.\n\nLet me revert my TOOLS.md change to simplify it back.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"刚搞复杂了 🫠 明白了，直接说目标，不加水：\n\n- ✅ 「更新qa服」→「开始更新qa服」\n- ✅ 「更新1v1_test服」→「开始更新1v1_test服」\n- ✅ 「更新测试服」→「开始更新测试服」\n\n就这样，不改。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":72347,"output":217,"cacheRead":6272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78836,"cost":{"input":0.01012858,"output":0.00006076,"cacheRead":0.000175616,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010364956}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779192035099,"responseId":"cb152cdc-9fff-4308-bb1e-a6bb6243004f"}}
