{"type":"message","id":"033948de","parentId":"54deb8c9","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:03:25.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script ran but with no output, which likely means it hit an error or timeout before logging anything. This might be a Node.js module issue (import syntax in ESM) when running directly. Let me try a different approach - write a script that works.\n\nBut actually, I already have the key information from the earlier analysis. The `dest` field in the pipeline's trigger form shows:\n- Current value: `1v1_qa`\n- The select component is an Ant Design searchable dropdown\n- The label is \"目标目录\"\n\nAnd from the build history, I know these dest values have been used:\n- `1v1_cehua2` (敖亚军's build #1083)\n- `1v1_qa` (our builds #1084, #1085)\n\nLet me try a simpler approach to read the page.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_osymn5CwE0bAXhvOZRJU9422","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const { chromium } = require('playwright');\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('devops_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\n(async () => {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ ignoreHTTPSErrors: true, viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 } });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  \n  // Click trigger button\n  const btn = page.locator('button', { hasText: '启动新构建' }).first();\n  await btn.click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));\n  \n  // Click dest search field to open dropdown\n  const destField = page.locator('[name=\"rc_select_0\"]').first();\n  await destField.click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  \n  // Get