{"type":"message","id":"e6315ea6","parentId":"fbd26a86","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:04:14.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script isn't producing output. It seems like it's failing or timing out. Let me try a simpler script that logs along the way.\n\nLooking at the earlier successful run (check_dest_vars.mjs), the .mjs file with `import` did work fine. The issue might be with the antd select component interaction.\n\nLet me try a different approach. I know from the earlier successful run that:\n1. The dest field has a value of \"1v1_qa\" (visible in the form)\n2. It uses an antd searchable select (rc_select_0)\n3. The label says \"目标目录\"\n\nThe key question from the user is what the available server names are in the pipeline. From the build history (#1083 by 敖亚军 used `dest=1v1_cehua2`), I know at least two options exist.\n\nActually, I think the user might be saying something simpler. They're saying \"查看一下流水线里面的服务器名字\" - check the server name inside the pipeline. The pipeline's actual server/directory names in the dest dropdown are the real server identifiers.\n\nSince I can't easily get the dropdown to open via headless playwright, let me try a different approach - search the page for all possible dest values that might be rendered.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7dyZlFo2zBlTB0B7nC1U6143","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('devops_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nasync function main() {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ ignoreHTTPSErrors: true, viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 } });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  \n  await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  \n  // Click trigger button\n  await page.locator('button', { hasText: '启动新构建' }).first().click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));\n  \n  // Get all text from the page\n  const bodyText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText);\n  console.log('BODY:', bodyText.substring(0, 10000));\n  \n  // Look for all text in the modal\n  const modalText = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const m = document.querySelector('.ant-modal, [class*=\"modal\"], [class*=\"dialog\"]');\n    return m ? m.innerText : 'no modal found';\n  });\n  console.log('\\nMODAL:', modalText);\n  \n  // Search for dest-related elements\n  const destElements = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const all = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n    const results = [];\n    for (const el of all) {\n      if (el.children.length === 0 && el.innerText && el.innerText.includes('1v1')) {\n        results.push(el.innerText.trim());\n      }\n    }\n    return [...new Set(results)];\n  });\n  console.log('\\n1v1-RELATED TEXTS:', JSON.stringify(destElements));\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('ERROR:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\check_dest_vars3.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":70,"output":829,"cacheRead":87296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88195,"cost":{"input":0.000009800000000000001,"output":0.00023212000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0024442879999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002686208}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192246225,"responseId":"b1465af9-8369-4fc4-a8c1-dbea4e671f69"}}
