{"type":"message","id":"c820023a","parentId":"665120ce","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:04:32.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see clearly! The form shows:\n\n```\ndest = 1v1_qa    (目标目录)\ncode_branch = YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521  (1.0分支 默认: master)\nbattle_branch = YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521 (1.0分支:YYZY_1V1_V1.0)\nconfig_branch = YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0521 (配置分支 开发分支:main)\nmanzo_branch = main (manzo分支 默认main 提审Branch_c0a7b016)\n```\n\nSo the `dest` variable's current visible value is `1v1_qa`. The label says \"目标目录\". But I still can't see the full dropdown options to know all available server names.\n\nThe dropdown is an Ant Design `rc_select` component which loads dynamically. When I click on it, I need to wait for the options to appear. Maybe the issue is that in headless mode, the dropdown popup uses a portal and isn't directly under the select.\n\nLet me try to click the select and then wait and search for the dropdown options.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_M8Tzuwr7e6eOkxfMZobk1172","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('devops_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nasync function main() {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ ignoreHTTPSErrors: true, viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 } });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  \n  await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  \n  // Click trigger button\n  await page.locator('button', { hasText: '启动新构建' }).first().click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));\n  \n  // The dest field might be a custom component. Try clicking the parent element that shows \"1v1_qa\"\n  // First, find all clickable elements near the dest value\n  const destClicks = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const allText = document.evaluate('//*[text()=\"1v1_qa\"]', document, null, XPathResult.ORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE, null);\n    const results = [];\n    for (let i = 0; i < allText.snapshotLength; i++) {\n      const el = allText.snapshotItem(i);\n      results.push({\n        tag: el.tagName,\n        className: el.className.substring(0, 80),\n        text: el.innerText.substring(0, 50),\n        html: el.outerHTML.substring(0, 200)\n      });\n    }\n    return results;\n  });\n  console.log('DEST_ELEMENTS:', JSON.stringify(destClicks, null, 2));\n  \n  // Try clicking on the first \"1v1_qa\" element's parent\n  const firstDest = page.locator('text=1v1_qa').first();\n  const parent = firstDest.locator('..');\n  await parent.click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));\n  \n  // Now look for dropdown items everywhere in DOM\n  const allOptions = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const all = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n    const texts = [];\n    for (const el of all) {\n      if (el.children.length === 0 && el.innerText.trim().startsWith('1v1')) {\n        texts.push(el.innerText.trim());\n      }\n    }\n    return [...new Set(texts)];\n  });\n  console.log('\\nALL 1v1 TEXTS:', JSON.stringify(allOptions));\n  \n  // Look for Ant Design select dropdown list\n  const antdSelect = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const popups = document.querySelectorAll('[class*=\"dropdown\"], [class*=\"popup\"], [class*=\"rc-select-dropdown\"]');\n    return Array.from(popups).map(p => p.innerText.trim().substring(0, 500));\n  });\n  console.log('\\nPOPUPS:', JSON.stringify(antdSelect));\n  \n  await page.screenshot({ path: 'form_screenshot.png' });\n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('ERROR:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\check_dest_vars3.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":892,"output":1108,"cacheRead":88320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90320,"cost":{"input":0.00012488,"output":0.00031024000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0024729599999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00290808}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192262700,"responseId":"d4c81a48-582f-47d1-96d6-a7291c64e275"}}
