{"type":"message","id":"e8212735","parentId":"37df905b","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:04:47.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script seems to hang when trying to click the parent element. It might be that the click doesn't properly open the dropdown because of the custom select component. Let me kill it and try a different approach.\n\nActually, I already got good info from the first successful run. The pipeline form shows the dest options are hidden in the Ant Design searchable select. The options aren't directly in the DOM as static HTML - they get loaded dynamically.\n\nFrom the earlier analysis, I know:\n- The pipeline has a `dest` variable that takes values like `1v1_qa`, `1v1_cehua2`, etc.\n- These are directories on the server: `/data/1v1_qa/`, `/data/1v1_cehua2/`, etc.\n- The label says \"目标目录\"\n\nBut I still don't have the full list of available dest options. Let me kill the hanging process and try a simpler query approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tackK3JlPnLOusZI4zUi4656","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"quiet-slug"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":134,"output":257,"cacheRead":90368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90759,"cost":{"input":0.00001876,"output":0.00007196000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002530304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002621024}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192284342,"responseId":"110c64dc-5675-4e4d-9306-f308f5eb61f7"}}
