{"type":"message","id":"bd893a96","parentId":"cdca9348","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:04:56.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The dest field is an ant-select-selection-item with title=\"1v1_qa\". The click on parent failed because it went to the wrong element. Let me try clicking the ant select component directly, not the inner span.\n\nActually, let me step back. The user said \"查看一下流水线里面的服务器名字\". They want me to check what server names are in the pipeline's dest dropdown. The select shows `1v1_qa` which is the current/default value. I need to open the dropdown to see all options.\n\nIn Ant Design, the select component structure is typically:\n```html\n<div class=\"ant-select\">\n  <div class=\"ant-select-selector\">\n    <span class=\"ant-select-selection-item\">1v1_qa</span>\n  </div>\n  <span class=\"ant-select-arrow\">...</span>\n</div>\n```\n\nAnd when clicked, a dropdown popup is appended to `document.body` with class `ant-select-dropdown`.\n\nLet me try a simpler approach - click on the ant-select parent div of the selection-item.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GjIH4QN0Xow0OsU7B0Qf3353","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('devops_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nasync function main() {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ ignoreHTTPSErrors: true, viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 } });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  \n  await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  await page.locator('button', { hasText: '启动新构建' }).first().click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));\n  \n  // Click the ant-select parent to open dropdown\n  const antSelect = page.locator('.ant-select').first();\n  await antSelect.click();\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  \n  // Find the dropdown list - it might be appended to body\n  const dropdownItems = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const dropdowns = document.querySelectorAll('.ant-select-dropdown');\n    const results = [];\n    for (const dd of dropdowns) {\n      const items = dd.querySelectorAll('.ant-select-item, [class*=\"item-option\"]');\n      for (const item of items) {\n        results.push(item.innerText.trim());\n      }\n    }\n    return results;\n  });\n  console.log('DROPDOWN ITEMS:', JSON.stringify(dropdownItems));\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('ERROR:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\check_dest_vars3.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":340,"output":720,"cacheRead":90752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91812,"cost":{"input":0.000047600000000000005,"output":0.00020160000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002541056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002790256}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192289709,"responseId":"0f3b42de-d790-45f0-a54c-049c32bdf811"}}
