{"type":"message","id":"9e908150","parentId":"8cafd2b2","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:05:12.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the available dest options! The dropdown items are:\n\n1. `1v1_test` - 自测服\n2. `1v1_dev` - 开发服\n3. `1v1_zhuanxiang` - 专项服\n4. `1v1_qa` - QA测试服\n5. `1v1_cehua1` - 策划服1\n6. `1v1_cehua2` - 策划服2\n\nSo the full list of available server names in the pipeline's dest dropdown:\n- **1v1_test** \n- **1v1_dev**\n- **1v1_zhuanxiang** (专项)\n- **1v1_qa** (QA)\n- **1v1_cehua1** (策划1)\n- **1v1_cehua2** (策划2)\n\nI think the user's point is: when they say \"更新qa服\", the actual server name in the pipeline is `1v1_qa`. So I should say \"开始更新1v1_qa服\" instead of \"开始更新qa服\".\n\nLet me update the TOOLS.md and MEMORY.md with this understanding.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！流水线 `dest` 可选值有 **6 个**：\n\n| 流水线名字 | 中文 |\n|-----------|------|\n| `1v1_test` | 自测服 |\n| `1v1_dev` | 开发服 |\n| `1v1_zhuanxiang` | 专项服 |\n| **`1v1_qa`** | **QA测试服** |\n| `1v1_cehua1` | 策划服1 |\n| `1v1_cehua2` | 策划服2 |\n\n所以主人说的「更新qa服」→ 实际叫 **1v1_qa** 服，对吧？\n\n反馈规则应该是：\n- 你说「更新qa服」→ 我反馈「开始更新 **1v1_qa** 服」\n- 你说「更新测试服」→ 我反馈「开始更新测试服」\n- 你说「更新1v1_test服」→ 我反馈「开始更新 **1v1_test** 服」\n\n是按流水线里的 **dest 值** 来反馈，对吧？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":153,"output":492,"cacheRead":91904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92549,"cost":{"input":0.00002142,"output":0.00013776,"cacheRead":0.002573312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002732492}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779192307347,"responseId":"7951e0e7-db81-43c1-82bf-d1f1006c4f42"}}
