{"type":"message","id":"4c6571d2","parentId":"929b97cf","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:06:18.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear understanding:\n\n1. **更新测试服** (original skill) → 特指**客户端**热更 (Unity hotupdate pipeline)\n2. **1v1-测试服流水线** (new DevOps pipeline) → **服务端**更新，通过 dest 参数指定目标服务器\n3. 如果不确定，问一下是客户端还是服务端\n\nSo the two skills are completely different:\n- \"更新测试服\" = Unity hotupdate (客户端热更)\n- \"更新qa服\" / \"更新1v1_qa服\" = DevOps pipeline (服务端)\n\nLet me update TOOLS.md, MEMORY.md, and the skill files to reflect this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完全明白了！现在两条线彻底分清了 🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9VJB4U1xAOmePwRPlp7G2966","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### 更新测试服 / 指定服 (Update Test Server)\n\n**触发指令:** \"更新测试服\" / \"更新qa服\" / \"构建1v1_qa服\"\n\n**反馈规范:** 请求说什么服就反馈什么服，不要改说法。完成后通知指派人。\n- 流水线全称是 **1v1-测试服**，反馈时必须说完整\n- 如「更新qa服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服」\n- 如「更新1v1_test服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标1v1_test服」\n\n**流程:\"","newText":"### 更新测试服（客户端热更）\n\n**触发指令:** \"更新测试服\"\n**本质:** Unity 热更流水线，更新客户端资源/代码\n**流程:"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":305,"output":440,"cacheRead":92544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93289,"cost":{"input":0.0000427,"output":0.0001232,"cacheRead":0.0025912319999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002757132}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192374037,"responseId":"db9f4a2e-9864-4375-8839-48c91b9d7c3a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"54d7b845","parentId":"4c6571d2","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:06:19.056Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_9VJB4U1xAOmePwRPlp7G2966","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\TOOLS.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\\n\\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\\n\\n## What Goes Here\\n\\nThings like:\\n\\n- Camera names and locations\\n- SSH hosts and aliases\\n- Preferred voices for TTS\\n- Speaker/room names\\n- Device nicknames\\n- Anything environment-specific\\n\\n## Examples\\n\\n```markdown\\n### Cameras\\n\\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\\n\\n### SSH\\n\\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\\n\\n### TTS\\n\\n- Preferred voice: \\\"Nova\\\" (warm, slightly British)\\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\\n```\\n\\n## Why Separate?\\n\\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\\n\\n---\\n\\nAdd whateve\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\n\n## What Goes Here\n\nThings like:\n\n- Camera names and locations\n- SSH hosts and aliases\n- Preferred voices for TTS\n- Speaker/room names\n- Device nicknames\n- Anything environment-specific\n\n## Examples\n\n```markdown\n### Cameras\n\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\n\n### SSH\n\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\n\n### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n```\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whateve\n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779192379056}}
