{"type":"message","id":"4fc21bc8","parentId":"81b661aa","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:06:24.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full context. Let me re-read the TOOLS.md section around line 63-75 to get the exact text. The oldText I need is from line 63 to line 71 (including the feedback spec). But actually the old text has changed - it now says \"反馈规范...\" which was from my previous edit. Let me update it properly.\n\nI need to read the full section to get the exact text.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_c2XY0qUjkY4AHlEKBMFc7760","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","offset":59,"limit":80}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":996,"output":183,"cacheRead":93696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94875,"cost":{"input":0.00013944,"output":0.000051240000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0026234879999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028141679999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192381266,"responseId":"f002184c-d020-49b4-9ecc-6c6290658020"}}
{"type":"message","id":"00a81b82","parentId":"4fc21bc8","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:06:24.107Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_c2XY0qUjkY4AHlEKBMFc7760","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Skills (My Custom Workflows)\n\n**群聊规范:** 每次在群里收到 @消息时，先立即回复一句礼貌性回应（如\"收到\"\"好的\"\"来了\"等），再开始处理需求。不要让群里的人等着没反应。\n\n### 更新测试服 / 指定服 (Update Test Server)\n\n**触发指令:** \"更新测试服\" / \"更新qa服\" / \"构建1v1_qa服\"\n\n**反馈规范:** 请求说什么服就反馈什么服，不要改说法。完成后通知指派人。\n- 流水线全称是 **1v1-测试服**，反馈时必须说完整\n- 如「更新qa服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服」\n- 如「更新1v1_test服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标1v1_test服」\n\n**流程:**\n1. 检查 Unity 热更流水线是否正在执行（通过进程命令行参数 `RunHotUpdatePipeline` 判断），如果有则提示已有流水线在执行，退出任务（这是主 agent 和 sub-agent 的双重检查）\n2. 关掉所有已打开的 Unity Editor 进程（kill Unity.exe 进程），避免项目被占用\n3. `git pull` 更新 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon` 当前分支\n4. 运行 Unity 工程 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv` 的 BuildPipeline 中的 \"热更\" 流水线（包含打资源 + 上传CDN）\n5. 更新完成后在群里 @兵王(周以天) 通知更新完成\n\n**反馈要求:** 每个步骤执行中状态变化都要通过飞书消息及时反馈，包括：开始执行、执行中（等待）、执行完成/失败。不要让主人干等。\n\n**更新完成后:** 用 `node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs` 发群消息通知（不要用 sessions_send，那只能发私聊）。\n成功命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n失败命令：`node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-fail`\n⚠️ 不要在命令行里拼含引号的 @ 文本，改用模板名（hotupdate-ok / hotupdate-fail）避免转义问题\n\n**实现方式:** 主 agent 只做快速操作（检查 + git pull），然后通过 sessions_spawn 创建 sub-agent 去跑 Unity 流水线。主 agent 立即释放，继续响应其他消息。sub-agent 在后台执行并监控日志，完成后自动汇报结果。\n\n**⚠️ 重要：sub-agent 必须通过 bat 文件执行，不要拼内联 PowerShell 命令！**\n`spawn UNKNOWN` 是 Windows 底层创建进程失败的错误，多行内联 PowerShell 脚本通过 exec 直接传入会导致此问题。\n\n**正确写法 (sub-agent 内的 exec 命令):**\n```\n\"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"\n```\n**无需包裹 cmd /c 或 powershell -Command**，exec 工具会直接启动 bat。\n\n**快捷命令 (手动执行):**\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n```\n\n**手动执行 (bat):**\n`E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\n\n**参数说明:**\n- Unity 路径: `C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe`\n- 流水线入口: `YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`\n- 流水线名称: \"热更\"（在 BuildPipeline 窗口配置）\n- CDN Git 根目录、渠道、版本等参数需在 Unity Editor 的 EditorConfig 中预先配置\n\n**注意:**\n- 首次使用需在 Unity Editor 中打开 BuildPipeline 窗口配置好 \"热更\" 流水线的各步骤参数\n- 运行需要管理员权限（Unity 许可证校验）\n- 完整的日志会输出到 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log`\n- **默认使用增量构建模式**（不清理 Bundles 缓存），速度更快。仅当资源丢失或异常时才需手动全量构建\n\n### 群组信息\n\n- **月圆之夜CCG开发群** → `oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77`\n  - 用途：更新测试服后在此群 @兵王(周以天) 通知\n  - 兵王(周以天) open_id：`ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966`\n  - 小骑士(谭佳钦) open_id：`ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3`\n  \n### 飞书消息 @ 人规范\n\n真正的 @ 提及格式：`<at user_id=\"open_id\">显示名字</at>`\n- ⚠️ `user_id` 属性值**必须用英文双引号包裹**，缺引号飞书不解析，变成普通文字\n- ⚠️ `<at>` 里的名字只是展示用兜底，飞书实际会按 `user_id` 自动解析成用户真实显示名\n- ✅ 正确示例：`<at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>`\n- ❌ 之前用的 `@$open_id$` 是假的，不会触发真实提醒，只会显示成文字\n- ❌ 纯文本 `@名字` 也只是文字，不会触发提醒\n- **先确认名字再拼**：如果不知道用户显示名，可以在聊天记录里找到对方被正确 @ 时的格式，或者手动确认\n\n### 打卡位置\n\n- **梅陇四村** (主人住所/打卡点)\n  - 经度: 121.421920\n  - 纬度: 31.138598\n\n[5 more lines in file. Use offset=139 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779192384107}}
{"type":"message","id":"233f4950","parentId":"00a81b82","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:06:28.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. I need to:\n\n1. Split the current \"更新测试服 / 指定服\" section into two separate sections:\n   - \"更新测试服 (客户端热更)\" - the original Unity hotupdate pipeline\n   - \"更新1v1服务器 (服务端DevOps)\" - the new DevOps pipeline\n\n2. Update MEMORY.md with the clarification\n3. Update the skill file\n\nLet me rewrite the TOOLS.md section.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GXhzNuWSn8Ev4Ba2iXhO9847","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### 更新测试服 / 指定服 (Update Test Server)\n\n**触发指令:** \"更新测试服\" / \"更新qa服\" / \"构建1v1_qa服\"\n\n**反馈规范:** 请求说什么服就反馈什么服，不要改说法。完成后通知指派人。\n- 流水线全称是 **1v1-测试服**，反馈时必须说完整\n- 如「更新qa服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标qa服」\n- 如「更新1v1_test服」→「开始更新1v1-测试服流水线，目标1v1_test服」\n\n**流程:」","newText":"### 更新测试服（客户端热更）\n\n**触发指令:** \"更新测试服\"\n**本质:** Unity 热更流水线，更新客户端资源/代码\n**完成后:** 在开发群 @兵王(周以天) 通知\n\n**流程:」"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1452,"output":401,"cacheRead":94848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96701,"cost":{"input":0.00020328000000000002,"output":0.00011228,"cacheRead":0.002655744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029713039999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192384110,"responseId":"81d0124f-7337-4f2e-9c9b-6645f1b321ff"}}
