{"type":"message","id":"7467b108","parentId":"e0a5da3b","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:13:22.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The user wants to:\n1. Rename the skill \"更新1v1服务器\" to \"更新服务器\" (more generic)\n2. When user says \"更新qa服务器\", I should look in DevOps under the \"1v1\" group's \"更新测试服\" build/pipeline for the `1v1_qa` server option\n\nSo the new skill should be generic enough to handle any server update task, and when given a name like \"qa服务器\", it should know how to find the right pipeline and the right dest value.\n\nLet me think about this:\n- The skill name becomes \"更新服务器\" (generic)\n- The skill needs to support different products/projects (currently just 1v1, but could expand)\n- When user says \"更新qa服务器\" (without specifying 1v1), look in the 1v1 pipeline for `1v1_qa`\n- This implies there might be other products in the future that have their own pipelines\n\nLet me update:\n1. Skill directory name might need to change from `update-test-server` to `update-server`\n2. SKILL.md content - generalize, add 1v1 as a sub-section\n3. TOOLS.md - update the section\n4. MEMORY.md - update\n5. COLLEAGUE_WHITELIST.md - update\n\nLet me start.明白！把技能改通用，1v1 作为子分类。我来操作 🌸\n\nFirst, let me look at the current SKILL.md to understand the full structure:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01RMgVSrBYaKppkc6QhhTmxE","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\update-test-server\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-opus-4-7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192791928,"responseId":"chatcmpl-93c7e391-184c-4e23-a8eb-c9482022cc01"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e3305f1","parentId":"7467b108","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:13:22.888Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01RMgVSrBYaKppkc6QhhTmxE","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: update-test-server\ndescription: Update the 1v1 server via DevOps CI/CD pipeline. Use when user says \"更新qa服\", \"更新1v1_qa服\", \"更新1v1_test服\", \"更新1v1_cehua2服\".\n---\n\n# 更新1v1服务器（服务端DevOps）\n\n通过 DevOps 流水线触发「1v1-测试服」构建，更新 1v1 服务端。\n\n**⚠️ 这是服务端更新，区别于客户端的「更新测试服」热更。如果需求方语意不明确，先确认是客户端还是服务端。**\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- **DevOps Cookie:** `workspace/devops_cookies.json`（需提前扫码登录保存）\n- **Playwright:** 已安装\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### 触发构建（默认 QA 服）\n\n```javascript\n// 参考脚本逻辑\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\n```\n\n### 操作步骤\n\n1. **读取 Cookie**：从 `workspace/devops_cookies.json` 加载\n2. **访问流水线**：`https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n3. **点击「启动新构建」**\n4. **设置目标参数**：\n   - `dest` = `1v1_qa`（QA 服）或 `1v1_cehua2`（策划测试服）\n   - `code_branch` / `battle_branch` / `config_branch` = 保持默认分支\n   - `manzo_branch` = 保持默认（main）\n5. **提交触发**并确认构建进入运行中状态\n6. **汇报结果**：返回构建编号和状态\n\n## Pipeline 详情\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 流水线名 | 1v1-测试服 |\n| 分组 | 1v1 |\n| Pipeline ID | `p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a` |\n| 描述 | 1v1测试服的维护 |\n| 当前版本 | 150+ |\n| 代码源 | GitLab（只读） |\n| 触发方式 | 手动触发 |\n\n### 构建步骤\n\n1. **打配置** — 拉配置分支 → Luban 编译 Excel 配表 → 输出到部署目录\n2. **build+替换** — 拉代码分支 → 编译 .NET 服务 → 复制 `.dll` 到部署目录\n3. **重启服务** — `stop.py` 停服务 → `run.py` 启动微服务\n\n### 启动变量\n\n| 变量名 | 常用值 | 说明 |\n|-------|--------|------|\n| `dest` | `1v1_qa`, `1v1_cehua2`, `1v1_test` ... | **目标部署目录（关键参数）**，支持任意合法服务器目录名 |\n| `code_branch` | 默认分支 | 代码分支，可自定义 |\n| `battle_branch` | 默认分支 | 战斗模块分支，可自定义 |\n| `config_branch` | 默认分支 | 配置分支，可自定义 |\n| `manzo_branch` | `main` | manzo 分支 |\n\n**dest 可选值（流水线里的服务器名）：**\n| 值 | 说明 |\n|----|------|\n| `1v1_test` | 自测服 |\n| `1v1_dev` | 开发服 |\n| `1v1_zhuanxiang` | 专项服 |\n| `1v1_qa` | QA测试服 |\n| `1v1_cehua1` | 策划服1 |\n| `1v1_cehua2` | 策划服2 |\n\n`dest` 支持以上 6 个值，流水线会将编译产物部署到 `/data/{dest}/` 下。\n\n**自定义分支：** 如果在请求中指定了分支值，则覆盖对应变量默认值。\n\n## Cookie 保活\n\nDevOps cookie 会自动保活（每天一次），无需手动重新登录。\n\n## 通知\n\n构建完成后，通知**指派人**（是谁叫我干活的就通知谁）。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- **这是更新服务端的流水线**（不是客户端热更），编译 .NET 服务并重启微服务\n- 触发后构建大约需要 **2 分钟**完成\n- `dest` 参数决定部署到哪个服务器\n- 如果 cookies 失效，需要带 `headless: false` 重新扫码登录\n- Pipeline 页面不支持修改配置（只读权限）\n- **反馈用流水线里的 dest 值**：如说「更新qa服」→反馈「开始更新1v1_qa服」\n- **不确定时问一句：是客户端还是服务端？**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779192802888}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9adf7e5","parentId":"8e3305f1","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:13:30.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I'll rewrite the SKILL.md to be more generic - \"更新服务器\" that handles different products. The 1v1 project is one product, but the skill is now more generic so we can add more products in the future.\n\nLet me also rename the skill directory. But first, let me create the new content."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_011JpYkLute8C27ThCAgvAmL","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -Force C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\update-server 2>&1","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-opus-4-7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779192802890,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2f118672-8ae5-4d3b-8bb6-273fb0093882"}}
