{"type":"message","id":"bb3c496a","parentId":"55d0d129","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:20:20.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The user is asking why I misunderstood when they @'d me in a group. This is happening in a Feishu direct chat, but they're referring to a group chat interaction.\n\nI don't have direct visibility into what happened in the group chat. Let me check the recent group activity and try to figure out what went wrong.\n\nActually, looking at the timestamps and context - the user might be referring to recent group messages. Since I have access to Feishu via the bot, I can check.\n\nBut first, let me think about what could have gone wrong. The user said \"更新qa服\" or similar in a group chat, and I might have:\n1. Interpreted it as something else\n2. Used wrong feedback wording\n3. Triggered wrong skill (client vs server)\n\nLet me check what I sent to the group recently.主人能告诉我具体是哪条消息我理解错了吗？我看一下群里的聊天记录："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01DmwM8iWFBkdT15a1yjQjA9","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\fetch_recent_group_msgs.mjs","content":"// Fetch recent group messages to see what user @ me about\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVpgH7h4UP7cVPfZRHh72E3jEOGKv';\n\nasync function main() {\n  const tokenRes = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const tokenData = await tokenRes.json();\n  if (tokenData.code !== 0) { console.error('Token failed:', tokenData); return; }\n  const token = tokenData.tenant_access_token;\n\n  const chatId = 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77'; // 月圆之夜CCG开发群\n  const res = await fetch(\n    `https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=chat_id&container_id=${chatId}&container_id_type=chat&page_size=30&sort_type=ByCreateTimeDesc`,\n    { headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}` } }\n  );\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) { console.error('Failed:', JSON.stringify(data)); return; }\n\n  console.log(`Found ${data.data?.items?.length || 0} messages\\n`);\n  for (const msg of data.data?.items || []) {\n    const time = new Date(parseInt(msg.create_time)).toLocaleString('zh-CN', { timeZone: 'Asia/Shanghai' });\n    const content = msg.body?.content || '';\n    const senderId = msg.sender?.id || '';\n    const senderType = msg.sender?.sender_type || '';\n    console.log(`[${time}] ${senderType}=${senderId.substring(0, 16)} (${msg.msg_type}):`);\n    console.log(`  ${content.substring(0, 300)}\\n`);\n  }\n}\n\nmain().catch(console.error);\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-opus-4-7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779193202762,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3075d777-a11f-41f8-b013-ccf2f0f035f4"}}
