{"type":"message","id":"4ca20960","parentId":"280e4858","timestamp":"2026-05-19T13:04:43.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to see the skill list. I should check the available skills and also my custom workflows from TOOLS.md to give a comprehensive view.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是目前我有的技能列表 🌸\n\n## 🚀 系统 Skills\n\n| 技能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **feishu-doc** | 飞书文档读写 |\n| **feishu-drive** | 飞书云盘文件管理 |\n| **feishu-perm** | 飞书文档权限管理 |\n| **feishu-wiki** | 飞书知识库导航 |\n| **tapd-bug-create** | TAPD 自动提单（缺陷/需求） |\n| **taskflow** | 多步骤持久化任务编排 |\n\n## 🛠️ 自定义工作流\n\n| 指令 | 做什么 | 通知谁 |\n|------|-------|-------|\n| **更新测试服** | Unity 客户端热更 | 开发群 @兵王 |\n| **更新服务器** | DevOps 服务端更新（默认 1v1）| 指派人 |\n| **更新qa/自测/策划服** | 同上，指定 dest 参数 | 指派人 |\n| **提单/提Bug/提需求** | TAPD 自动创建 | 不通知 |\n| **重启** | OpenClaw 网关重启 | 不通知 |\n\n## 👥 同事可用（白名单）\n\n| 任务 | 范围 |\n|------|------|\n| 更新测试服 | 客户端热更 |\n| 更新服务器 | 服务端（qa/test/策划/开发/专项/策划1/策划2）|\n| 提单 | TAPD 创建缺陷 |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":112168,"output":361,"cacheRead":6272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118801,"cost":{"input":0.015703520000000002,"output":0.00010108,"cacheRead":0.000175616,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015980216000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779195874504,"responseId":"1f8d1e5a-5dde-4322-b5c5-19322ec5fcb1"}}
