{"type":"message","id":"24244d0f","parentId":"6e9adefa","timestamp":"2026-05-19T13:06:35.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the skill is created. Now let me check if the skill-creator was properly read. Actually, let me also verify the skill shows up properly in the available_skills by reading it.\n\nAlso, I should update MEMORY.md to record this new skill creation, and the daily memory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"创建完成 🌸\n\n这次对话已经我记了今天的日志，所以顺便也把新建「记忆管家」技能这件事和今天的对话记录一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_8vHImQ8Z3iVOJBWjM7c01768","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## 网关自助重启脚本\n- 创建 `scripts/restart_gateway.ps1`，支持延迟重启不把自己杀掉\n- 主人说「重启」时直接用这个脚本\n- 已在 TOOLS.md 和 MEMORY.md 记录\n- 当前 session 是重启后的干净环境\n\n## 新建技能「memory-keeper」\n- SKILL.md 定义了每次对话结束时自动保存技能和记忆的逻辑\n- 分类归档到对应文件：TOOLS.md / MEMORY.md / 每日日志 / SKILL.md / 白名单\n- 只有在有新信息时才记录，不冗余","oldText":"## 网关自助重启脚本\n- 创建 `scripts/restart_gateway.ps1`，支持延迟重启不把自己杀掉\n- 主人说「重启」时直接用这个脚本\n- 已在 TOOLS.md 和 MEMORY.md 记录\n- 当前 session 是重启后的干净环境"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-05-19.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":76,"output":383,"cacheRead":120832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121291,"cost":{"input":0.000010640000000000001,"output":0.00010724000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003383296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003501176}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779195990779,"responseId":"779ed858-a627-40c2-b994-8b1ad9803371"}}
