{"type":"message","id":"eb06fec2","parentId":"159bec56","timestamp":"2026-05-19T13:06:38.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"技能「记忆管家（memory-keeper）」已创建 ✅\n\n路径：`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/memory-keeper/SKILL.md`\n\n核心逻辑：\n- 🧠 对话结束自动评估是否有新信息\n- 📂 新信息自动分类到对应文件（不都塞 MEMORY.md 一个文件）\n- ✂️ 旧规则被新规则完全覆盖时直接替换，不追加\n- 📋 主人说「更新技能和记忆」时强制触发\n\n以后我就不用每次都问「保存一下」啦 🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":121,"output":120,"cacheRead":121216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121457,"cost":{"input":0.00001694,"output":0.000033600000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0033940479999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034445879999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779195995723,"responseId":"bdddbca9-6cf7-4f1d-98b8-47faabda3264"}}
